definition:
A man of the tribe of Benjamin living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, only mentioned at Gen.46.21; 
 son of: Benjamin (H1144); 
 brother of: Bela (H1106A), Becher (H1071), Ashbel (H0788), Gera (H1617), Naaman (H5283), Ehi (H0278), Rosh (H7220), Muppim (H4649), Huppim (H2650H), Ahiram (H0297) and Jediael (H3043)
 § Ard = "I shall subdue"
1) son of Benjamin
2) grandson of Benjamin
